<div class="dice-roll swnr-mage-chat-roll-wrap">
  <div class="swnr-mage-chat-roll-content">
    <div class="dice-result">
      <h4 class="swnr-mage-chat-roll-section-title">Act of Hubris</h4>
      <h5 class="swnr-mage-chat-roll-section-subtitle">against {{rollType}} Wisdom</h5>
      <div class="dice-tooltip" style="display: none;">
        <div class="dice-formula swnr-mage-chat-roll-dice-formula">{{r.formula}}</div>
        <section class="tooltip-part">
          <div class="dice">
            <ol class="dice-rolls">
              {{#each r.dice as |dice|}}
              {{#each dice.results as |roll|}}
              <li class="roll die d10
                  {{#if roll.success}}success{{/if}}
                  {{#if roll.exploded}}exploded{{/if}}
                  ">{{roll.result}}</li>
              {{/each}}
              {{/each}}
            </ol>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <h4 class="dice-total swnr-mage-chat-roll-total-successes swnr-mage-chat-roll-result-{{successType}}">
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'exceptional'}}
        Exceptional Success
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'success'}}
        Successful
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'failure'}}
        Failure
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'dramafail'}}
        Dramatic Failure to Cast
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        <small>Successes: {{r.result}}</small>
      </h4>
      <p>
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'exceptional'}}
          Your character's Wisdom is reinforced by examining the risk and consequences of her actions. Take an additional Arcane Beat from the epiphany.
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'success'}}
          Your character is able to examine and understand the ramifications of her actions. She does not lose Wisdom.
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'failure'}}
          Your character loses a dot of Wisdom, as she fails to see the consequences and ripples from her actions. Take the Megalomaniacal or Rampant Condition.
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'dramafail'}}
          Your character not only loses a dot of Wisdom from her complete disregard for the world around her, but she also gains a Persistent Condition pertaining to the hubris. Take Megalomaniacal or Rampant. The normal resolution gives a Beat. Your character may only resolve the Condition permanently by gaining a dot of Wisdom.
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>